{"type": "article", "id": 8883, "title": "智能表盘该是圆的还是方的，三星又变卦了", "description": "为什么说是“又”？因为去年三星还换了两遍操作系统。", "date": "2015-04-24T14:42:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1233, "name": "智能手表"}, {"id": 9369, "name": "Gear"}, {"id": 9370, "name": "圆形表盘"}, {"id": 536, "name": "三星"}], "category": 4, "author": 43366, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223221MXdluTAKNF9JrzH3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t在 Gear S <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">已经把智能表的屏幕弄</span>“弯”之后，三星又打算把下一代 Gear <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的表盘换成圆形——这消息早在今年年初就由 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.sammobile.com/2015/01/08/exclusive-a-round-dial-samsung-smartwatch-is-in-the-works-mwc-release-likely/\" target=\"_blank\">SamMobile </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.sammobile.com/2015/01/08/exclusive-a-round-dial-samsung-smartwatch-is-in-the-works-mwc-release-likely/\" target=\"_blank\">曝光</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SamMobile </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当时称三星这款新的智能表代号为“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Orbis</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”，他们还<a href=\"http://www.sammobile.com/2015/01/14/exclusive-samsungs-round-smartwatch-to-have-a-rotating-bezel-ring-and-crown-shaped-power-button/\" target=\"_blank\">给出了更多细节</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Orbis</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”将会有一个表冠状的电源开关、可旋转的边框，甚至连“发布日期”都定了——</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月初的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">MWC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（<a href=\"http://www.mobileworldcongress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">世界移动大会，</a></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.mobileworldcongress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Mobile World Congress</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。尽管 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SamMobile </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这么“言之凿凿”，但这款圆形智能表最后并<a href=\"http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/news/wearable-tech/3594494/samsung-orbis-round-smartwatch-no-show-at-mwc/\" target=\"_blank\">没有现身</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t不过今天看起来这事似乎更靠谱了，三星<a href=\"http://www.samsungmobilepress.com/2015/04/24/Samsung-to-Release-SDK-for-Next-Generation-Gear\" target=\"_blank\">宣布将提前给开发者提供软件开发包</a>（<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SDK</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，在三星官网<a href=\"http://developer.samsung.com/wearable/\" target=\"_blank\">邀请网页</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">列举的所有应用，其界面</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全部都是圆形，可三星两年来发布的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">款智能手表的表盘均为方形。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223220TNQmSGV90eLJBqzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t同时，这是三星第一次提前开放智能手表的开发包，三星 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">IT </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和移动部门 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">CEO </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">申宗均解释称这是为了让开发者加入合作，“共同为智能移动生活提供独特的用户体验。”值得一提的是，在一同发布的下一代 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">智能表全球合作伙伴中百度地图位列其中。不过，这一“提前”的举动</span><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">也</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">似乎在暗示下一代 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">智能手表可能和之前有重大变化，需要开发者早做准备。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t此前摩托罗拉主打圆形表盘的智能表 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Moto 360 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">大受欢迎，去年的销量在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Android </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">阵营中独占鳌头。此后圆形表盘逐渐成为一股风潮，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">LG 去年 10 月紧跟着</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://gadgets.ndtv.com/wearables/news/lg-g-watch-r-android-wear-smartwatch-to-hit-shelves-on-october-14-603025\" target=\"_blank\">推出</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://gadgets.ndtv.com/wearables/news/lg-g-watch-r-android-wear-smartwatch-to-hit-shelves-on-october-14-603025\" target=\"_blank\">圆形表盘</a> LG R 系列，华为在上个月的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/3/3/8140837/huawei-watch-design-interview-mwc-2015\" target=\"_blank\">MWC </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/3/3/8140837/huawei-watch-design-interview-mwc-2015\" target=\"_blank\">上宣布</a> 6 月即将推出的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Huawei Watch </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会采用圆形表盘</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t可事实上，尽管三星推出智能表已近两年，但他们在“到底要做什么样的手表”这个问题上始终摇摆不定。\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t一直徘徊在 Tizen 和 Android 之间的操作系统\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t2013 <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">9 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月发布的第一代三星 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Galaxy Gear </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">智能表搭载的系统还是 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Android</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，但到了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年初的第二代，不仅名字换成 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear 2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear 2 Neo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，就连操作系统也改成了自家和 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Intel </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">联合开发的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Tizen </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t可同年 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月底发布的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear Live </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">刚回到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Android </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">阵营不久，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">9 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月的新一代 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear S </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">却又是一款 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Tizen </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手表。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;white-space:normal;\">其实三星</span><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;white-space:normal;\">一直以来</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;white-space:normal;\">就想拥有自己的操作系统，尽管是 Android 帮助三星夺取了手机霸主的地位，可也正是由于 Android，让三星陷入和不同层次的众多 Android 厂商苦斗的局面。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">由于自家的 Tizen 系统在手机上反响寥寥，三星一直希望通过智能手表来证明 Tizen，<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">公司高管在不同场合说过 Tizen 更适合可穿戴设备——因为它更省电。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">可相比于 Android，Tizen 的应用实在太少。2013 年的 MWC 上，知名跑步应用 RunKeeper 的开发人员<span style=\"color:#3D3C40;font-family:Lato, appleLogo, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;\">告诉《好奇心日报》，三星并未提供任何将应用从 Android 迁移到 Tizen 的帮助，因此他们暂时并没有为 Tizen 系统开发应用的计划。</span></span></span>过少的应用显然难以吸引用户，这让三星陷入两难。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t关于 Tizen 和 Android 的更多内容请<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/1268.html\" target=\"_blank\">戳这里阅读《好奇心日报》去年的 10 个图报道</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t硬件上，到底要不要有摄像头和 SIM 卡槽？\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t除了操作系统，在智能手表的硬件配置上三星也一变再变。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t即便同属三星的第二代智能表，<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear 2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">还延续着 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Galaxy Gear </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">配备摄像头的做法，只是把摄像头从表带转移到了表盘上方，可 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear 2 Neo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">却直接取消了摄像头。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t此外，从对待 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SIM </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡的态度上，更能看出三星并没有明确智能手表和手机的关系。作为三星最近一款智能表，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear S </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上首次配备了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Nano-SIM </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡卡槽，这也意味着它能独立接听电话，<a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2014/11/15/the-samsung-gear-s-is-a-smartphone-on-your-wrist/\" target=\"_blank\">完全脱离手机</a>，此前几乎所有厂商的智能手表均只是手机的配件。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t可两个月后，三星却又在日本发布了仅支持 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">WiFi </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的无卡槽 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gear S </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">版本，而新一代圆形表盘的智能表上是否还会有 SIM 卡卡槽还不得而知。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t也许三星这样的“反复无常”是想复制它在手机市场上曾经辉煌的“机海战术”，但这对尚未普及的智能手表来说显然不太合适。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t首先应用开发者难以为不同硬件配置的智能手表逐一适配，这极大影响用户体验。未来，方形界面极有可能换成圆形，三星的开发者来得及改吗？</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t同时对用户来说，面对完全陌生的智能手表，连三星自己都没弄清楚定位，怎么指望它像苹果那样一遍又一遍地告诉用户该怎么用？苹果对 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Apple Watch </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一直有着明确的定位：将人们从 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">iPhone </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中解放出来，利用 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Glance </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">等新的交互方式让人无需一遍遍地拿出手机就可以处理收到的重要通知，至少从<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/8273.html\" target=\"_blank\">《纽约时报》的评测</a>（<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/8273.html\" target=\"_blank\">戳这里看</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，无需翻墙）来看，苹果的良苦用心还是得到了用户的领悟。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">那么三星呢？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t首页图来源：<a href=\"http://www.movilzona.es/samsung/gear-2/\" target=\"_blank\">Movilzona</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://developer.samsung.com/wearable/\" target=\"_blank\">三星</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}